# 解决JSON反序列化错误和收藏服务实现问题

## 问题分析

1. **JSON反序列化错误**：错误表明系统尝试将JSON对象反序列化为Integer类型，但实际接收的是一个对象
2. **收藏服务实现问题**：`addCollection`方法存在逻辑错误，新建的列表没有保存回Map中

## 解决方案

### 1. 修复JSON反序列化问题

确保Controller方法的参数类型与前端发送的数据类型匹配：

```java
@RestController
@RequestMapping("/collection")
public class CollectionController {

    @Autowired
    private CollectionService collectionService;

    @PostMapping("/add")
    public Result addCollection(@RequestBody CollectionRequest request) {
        collectionService.addCollection(request.getUserId(), request.getProduct());
        return Result.success();
    }

    @PostMapping("/remove")
    public Result removeCollection(@RequestBody CollectionRequest request) {
        collectionService.delCollection(request.getUserId(), request.getProduct());
        return Result.success();
    }

    @GetMapping("/list")
    public Result getCollection(@RequestParam Integer userId) {
        List<Products> collections = collectionService.getCollection(userId);
        return Result.success(collections);
    }
}

@Data
class CollectionRequest {
    private Integer userId;
    private Products product;
}
```

### 2. 修复CollectionServiceImpl实现

```java
@Service
public class CollectionServiceImpl implements CollectionService {

    // 使用ConcurrentHashMap保证线程安全
    private final Map<Integer, List<Products>> collectionMap = new ConcurrentHashMap<>();

    @Override
    public List<Products> getCollection(Integer userId) {
        return collectionMap.getOrDefault(userId, new ArrayList<>());
    }

    @Override
    public void addCollection(Integer userId, Products product) {
        // 使用computeIfAbsent保证线程安全
        List<Products> productsList = collectionMap.computeIfAbsent(userId, k -> new ArrayList<>());

        // 检查是否已收藏
        boolean alreadyCollected = productsList.stream()
            .anyMatch(p -> p.getId().equals(product.getId()));

        if (!alreadyCollected) {
            productsList.add(product);
        }
    }

    @Override
    public void delCollection(Integer userId, Products product) {
        if (collectionMap.containsKey(userId)) {
            collectionMap.get(userId).removeIf(p -> p.getId().equals(product.getId()));
        }
    }
}
```

### 3. 添加必要的异常处理

```java
@ControllerAdvice
public class GlobalExceptionHandler {

    @ExceptionHandler(HttpMessageNotReadableException.class)
    @ResponseBody
    public Result handleHttpMessageNotReadableException(HttpMessageNotReadableException e) {
        log.error("请求参数解析错误", e);
        return Result.fail("请求参数格式不正确");
    }

    @ExceptionHandler(Exception.class)
    @ResponseBody
    public Result handleException(Exception e) {
        log.error("系统异常", e);
        return Result.fail("系统繁忙，请稍后再试");
    }
}
```

### 4. 确保Products类可序列化

```java
@Data
public class Products implements Serializable {
    private Integer id;
    private String name;
    private Double price;
    private Integer stock;
    private String category;
    private String imageUrl;
    private Integer status;
    private String createdAt;

    // 必须实现equals和hashCode方法，以便正确比较和删除
    @Override
    public boolean equals(Object o) {
        if (this == o) return true;
        if (o == null || getClass() != o.getClass()) return false;
        Products products = (Products) o;
        return Objects.equals(id, products.id);
    }

    @Override
    public int hashCode() {
        return Objects.hash(id);
    }
}
```

## 完整修复后的CollectionServiceImpl

```java
@Service
public class CollectionServiceImpl implements CollectionService {

    private final Map<Integer, List<Products>> collectionMap = new ConcurrentHashMap<>();

    @Override
    public List<Products> getCollection(Integer userId) {
        return Optional.ofNullable(collectionMap.get(userId))
                     .orElse(Collections.emptyList());
    }

    @Override
    public void addCollection(Integer userId, Products product) {
        Objects.requireNonNull(userId, "用户ID不能为空");
        Objects.requireNonNull(product, "商品不能为空");
        Objects.requireNonNull(product.getId(), "商品ID不能为空");

        List<Products> userCollections = collectionMap.computeIfAbsent(
            userId, 
            k -> new CopyOnWriteArrayList<>()
        );

        // 线程安全地添加商品
        synchronized (userCollections) {
            if (!userCollections.contains(product)) {
                userCollections.add(product);
            }
        }
    }

    @Override
    public void delCollection(Integer userId, Products product) {
        if (userId == null || product == null || product.getId() == null) {
            return;
        }

        List<Products> userCollections = collectionMap.get(userId);
        if (userCollections != null) {
            userCollections.removeIf(p -> product.getId().equals(p.getId()));
        }
    }

    @Override
    public boolean isCollected(Integer userId, Integer productId) {
        if (userId == null || productId == null) {
            return false;
        }

        List<Products> userCollections = collectionMap.get(userId);
        return userCollections != null && 
               userCollections.stream()
                   .anyMatch(p -> productId.equals(p.getId()));
    }
}
```

## 使用建议

1. 前端调用时确保发送正确的JSON格式：
   ```json
   // 添加收藏
   POST /collection/add
   {
     "userId": 123,
     "product": {
       "id": 456,
       "name": "玫瑰花",
       // 其他产品属性
     }
   }

   // 移除收藏
   POST /collection/remove
   {
     "userId": 123,
     "product": {
       "id": 456
     }
   }

   // 获取收藏列表
   GET /collection/list?userId=123
   ```

2. 对于生产环境，建议将收藏数据持久化到数据库而非内存中

3. 考虑添加分页功能，防止用户收藏列表过大

4. 可以添加收藏数量的限制，防止用户收藏过多商品

